high_descs: Turn around and find the coffee machine on the right side.
Pick up the knife from the the counter to the left of the coffee machine.
Carry the knife and turn around to the white table.
Place the knife in the cup beside the toaster.
Pick up the cup and knife from the table.
Carry the cup and turn around to go back to the coffee machine.
Place the cup and knife to the front left side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and cup to a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and take a few steps then turn right and walk to the area just to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up the knife that's under the spoon.
Turn around and walk to the other white table.
Put the knife in the orange cup the the toaster.
Pick up the orange cup with the knife in it.
Turn around and walk back to the other counter.
Put the cup near the bottom left corner of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: turn around, go to counter with blue coffee maker on the right
pick up knife under spoon on counter
turn around, go to table with toaster
place knife in orange goblet next to toaster
pick up goblet with knife
turn around, go to counter with coffee maker
place goblet on front, right corner of counter
anns.task_desc: Place goblet with knife on counter with coffee maker
